        "href": "https://github.com/AITOBIAS04/miroshark-aeon/pull/60",
        "source": "PR #60"
      }
    },
    "text_pr60": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "/api/feed.atom and /api/feed.rss serve the public gallery as standard syndication feeds with share-card PNG and replay GIF as media enclosures. Subscribe in Feedly, Readwise, Obsidian, or any RSS reader. 17 offline unit tests, zero new dependencies (stdlib XML). Converts the pull-based gallery into a push channel."
      }
    },
