      "props": {
        "text": "WONDERWALL_BASE_URL + WONDERWALL_API_KEY let operators route the 850+ agent-action calls to a self-hosted vLLM/Modal/fine-tune without touching other model slots. Cloud preset refreshed to Mimo V2 Flash + Grok-4.1 Fast (~$1/run). Best preset dropped."
      }
